{"tid":1211533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係金鐘嘅手足，留得青山在啊","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T16:10:49.000Z","uid":138946,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3260af6358b8c17bba0e97f41fb64fb4ee3123fd","tid":1211533,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:56:37.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我先。<br />\n今時唔同往日，警察已經係手持權力嘅暴徒，越夜越對佢地有利，你地睇。死守政總冇用，佢哋可以無限改期、甚至癲到用直升機都得。共產黨唔可以用我地慣有嘅邏輯去評估，癡撚線惡魔嚟㗎班友。<br />\n但我唔想，我真係唔想你地任何一個因為呢個戰略價值已經唔係幾高嘅地方，而受到任何損害、甚至冇咗性命。<br />\n手足們，請珍重。"},{"pid":"5c8b3bee6ddd7b948aee58259f74099654c093e0","tid":1211533,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:00:24.000Z","msg":"翻屋企啦手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔想望住你地死"},{"pid":"0fe08be6a5d160a23c2d7276202e8acbd21d976d","tid":1211533,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:01:41.000Z","msg":"唔好落單啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9535800e2a4fe04acd60f9fe002a6e011f10a76","tid":1211533,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fe08be6a5d160a23c2d7276202e8acbd21d976d","tid":1211533,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:01:41.000Z","msg":"唔好落單啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:05:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67063105db1e3754ef42f6f89d6cbfe4de5cd534","tid":1211533,"uid":211707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:10:49.000Z","msg":"推"}]}